<details>
<summary>Why a cohort and not 1:1 coaching?</summary>
<p>Two reasons. First, the peer dynamic. You learn faster watching 20 other operators apply the same framework to their different companies than you do being coached alone. Second, accountability — the cohort sees your homework. That's a stronger forcing function than a coach you can no-show.</p>
